Dayda

City of New York

This is a catalog of datasets organized and made more accessible from the City of New York, providing simple dowloadable CSV and JSON files, as well as Postman Collections you can use as part of workflows and other automation.

    Bridge Hold Location Stipulations

    This dataset provides locations which have the Bridge Hold as one of the stipulations. The information gives the location of all the blocks and the intersections within 100 feet of a Bridge Structure.
